Step 2: Update Check existing live file to filter by filename

Click Check existing live file
Click Show advanced options (link near the bottom)
Find the Filter Query field
Enter exactly:

   FileLeafRef eq 'CAP_to_BU_Mapping.xlsx'

Save

FileLeafRef is SharePoint's internal field name for the file's name. This filter makes the action return ONLY files with that exact name, in that folder — so we get either zero items (no live file) or one item (the live file). No folders, no other files.

Step 3: Revert Live file exists? to use Check existing live file directly

Click Live file exists?
Left side fx:

   length(body('Check_existing_live_file')?['value'])

Step 4: Revert Archive existing file to use Check existing live file directly

Click Archive existing file
File to Move fx:

   first(body('Check_existing_live_file')?['value'])?['{Identifier}']

That's it. No Filter array action, no template language fights. Save and test.
